WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.520 --> 00:00:01.360
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.360 --> 00:00:16.337
I’m going to go ahead and release this video to you.

00:00:16.337 --> 00:00:48.760
I talked to my pastor last night because I was curious about why the Lord was showing me dates and more depth to this.

00:00:48.760 --> 00:01:48.249
It’s like an onion; it has layers, and as you pull off the layers, you get to the core of what the Lord wants to talk to you about concerning this virus—this plague that's coming.

00:01:51.385 --> 00:02:16.542
To the seasoned prayer people who come on here and pray with me, thank you; I know you get this.

00:02:17.040 --> 00:03:08.279
To the ones who do not understand the beginnings of prayer and how to get in the rivers, stick around; I'm going to start praying a lot more on this channel.

00:03:08.279 --> 00:03:18.012
When I was in corporate prayer last night, the Lord showed how vital it is that the body of Christ join together as an army and pray together even more.

00:03:18.012 --> 00:03:35.612
He showed me that we were like a sharpened arrow with beautiful inscriptions written on it.

00:03:35.612 --> 00:03:53.280
He said, 'Brandon, you're like that arrow whenever you join together.

00:03:53.280 --> 00:04:12.125
' It was like a precise target; we hit it precisely.

00:04:12.125 --> 00:04:49.312
An arrow is made to hit the target and be very precise, especially one made by a good craftsman.

00:04:49.312 --> 00:05:19.060
I talked to Pastor Candace last night, and I said that I think it’s interesting the Lord revealed this to me again.

00:05:19.060 --> 00:05:45.555
This is the fourth time He has spoken to me about the virus, and He keeps giving me more detail.

00:05:45.555 --> 00:06:13.768
He showed me the 350 million and warned me about obesity and them using genocide.

00:06:13.768 --> 00:06:34.113
In the vision, I heard that they were going to try to act like Hitler.

00:06:34.113 --> 00:07:15.600
It was a demonic mindset of trying to get rid of obese people with ailments like high blood pressure and diabetes—things they considered a drain on society.

00:07:17.932 --> 00:07:41.434
That is why the Lord gave me a mandate about my weight over a year ago.

00:07:43.377 --> 00:08:06.160
He said, 'Brandon, this is what they're planning in the future; you're running out of time.

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:26.279
' In this last vision, the Lord downloaded more detail about the virus.

00:08:33.691 --> 00:09:16.535
I took it to Pastor Candace and told her that I didn't want to release another heavy warning vision right now, especially after the trucks and when nothing seemed to happen in the natural.

00:09:16.535 --> 00:09:37.463
But I know beyond a shadow of a doubt that the trucks and vans exist.

00:09:39.074 --> 00:09:46.679
The Lord said, 'This is not over.

00:09:46.679 --> 00:10:23.640
You must continue to pray, for you delayed what they were trying to do during the inauguration because the people joined together.

00:10:23.640 --> 00:10:49.394
' It went viral with Alex Jones, and millions of people prayed that President Trump would be protected.

00:10:53.615 --> 00:11:04.818
The fervent, effectual prayer of the righteous availeth much.

00:11:08.234 --> 00:11:45.573
I truly believe God is showing us another round of something the enemy is trying to do that is bigger even than terrorist activity.

00:11:45.573 --> 00:12:12.476
I saw in this vision millions upon millions of people perishing because of this virus.

00:12:12.476 --> 00:12:24.560
Why is He revealing it years in advance?

00:12:24.560 --> 00:12:41.560
To warn us about what's coming during President Trump's term.

00:12:41.560 --> 00:12:46.360
It’s a four-year window.

00:12:55.109 --> 00:12:55.297
The Lord said, 'You must pray now.

00:12:55.297 --> 00:13:25.876
' Pastor Candace said the Lord warns us in advance because it takes time to turn a major ship.

00:13:25.876 --> 00:14:05.880
If the Titanic had been warned in time, they could have turned and not hit the iceberg.

00:14:05.880 --> 00:14:11.937
I'm a Watchman on the wall.

00:14:11.937 --> 00:14:34.800
I'm not like Joseph Z or Troy black; I don't feel that about myself, though I may see prophetically.

00:14:34.800 --> 00:15:03.560
God has told me to pray and intercede to warn His people of what is coming to turn things throughout governments.

00:15:03.560 --> 00:15:35.339
I'm calling you to raise up a million-person prayer army to change events throughout the whole world.

00:15:35.339 --> 00:15:40.980
Good morning, family.

00:15:48.524 --> 00:15:53.393
I have a heavy word to give.

00:16:12.740 --> 00:17:06.079
I asked the Lord when He showed this to me, seeing Him dying on the cross, 'Father, when You knew what was coming and that they were going to crucify You, how did You not let that succumb You?

00:17:06.079 --> 00:17:19.079
How did You keep those thoughts from tormenting You?

00:17:19.079 --> 00:17:59.790
' He said, 'Brandon, I knew I had to talk to the people while it was day, because night was coming.

00:17:59.790 --> 00:18:07.600
' He focused on the task at hand and didn't let the future get inside of Him.

00:18:11.125 --> 00:18:20.737
He kept ministering because He saw the need.

00:18:31.698 --> 00:18:49.116
I asked the Lord how I could keep from letting the heaviness of these visions get inside of me.

00:18:50.076 --> 00:19:22.140
The Lord told me they're devising a plan right now with another plague, similar to the Black Death from the 1300s.

00:19:22.140 --> 00:19:30.080
Suddenly, I was taken to the past.

00:19:30.080 --> 00:19:46.085
I saw cobblestone streets and roofs made out of hay.

00:19:50.319 --> 00:20:10.400
I saw chickens, a blacksmith molding metal, and children in overalls.

00:20:10.400 --> 00:20:33.304
I saw women in bonnets and fires on stoves inside houses.

00:20:33.809 --> 00:20:54.236
I saw people who were scared of the Black Death.

00:20:54.236 --> 00:21:12.849
They weren't able to wash their hands and had no personal hygiene.

00:21:21.764 --> 00:21:42.255
The Lord emphasized looking at their hands; I could see the germs and the lack of antibacterial soap.

00:21:43.274 --> 00:21:49.429
It was an ominous feeling.

00:21:49.429 --> 00:22:05.700
I saw people with sheets over them, dead in the streets.

00:22:06.030 --> 00:22:33.276
The Lord said what’s about to happen is a type and shadow of the Black Death.

00:22:33.652 --> 00:23:12.511
I saw them using AI technology again to bring up a new strain of this Black Death.

00:23:36.700 --> 00:23:37.185
I saw three rats in a plexiglass box.

00:23:37.185 --> 00:23:54.671
They were testing a thick, yellow liquid in a vial.

00:23:54.671 --> 00:24:13.600
They injected the rats in the hindquarters and observed them.

00:24:13.600 --> 00:24:17.685
Two rats died quickly, but one did not.

00:24:17.685 --> 00:24:33.719
They released that type of rat into Europe.

00:24:34.946 --> 00:25:06.342
The Lord said the first round with COVID was with bats; now they will use rats because they're more mobile.

00:25:06.342 --> 00:26:00.750
As they were released, the infection spread, starting as a light red and getting darker as it went, looking like it was bleeding upon Europe, then Africa, and then the Middle East.

00:26:00.750 --> 00:26:37.863
I saw President Trump standing behind a podium saying we're blocking all international travel and suspending all air travel to stop this lethal thing.

00:26:37.863 --> 00:26:54.740
Then I saw the Euro collapse, triggering the collapse of the U.

00:26:54.740 --> 00:26:56.760
S.

00:26:56.760 --> 00:26:58.530
dollar.

00:26:59.655 --> 00:27:13.409
The whole economy is taken down by another virus.

00:27:20.849 --> 00:27:36.888
I saw people unable to get food, trying to raid others out of desperation.

00:27:36.888 --> 00:28:15.470
I saw a major factory with a burner stack, but the workers became fewer and fewer until they put caution tape on the doors.

00:28:18.543 --> 00:28:28.502
This happened over a couple of weeks.

00:28:28.502 --> 00:28:44.668
I saw people with semi-automatic weapons trying to raid homes for supplies.

00:29:01.232 --> 00:29:24.315
I saw the importance of having a well and a supply of food in the country, off the grid, and being watchful about who you tell.

00:29:24.315 --> 00:29:31.760
I saw death everywhere.

00:29:31.760 --> 00:29:37.109
It was awful.

00:29:40.497 --> 00:30:05.710
The Lord said 350 million is a small number compared to what they have planned for North America.

00:30:05.710 --> 00:30:36.360
If you look at the Black Death, it took out almost half the population—50 million people perished.

00:30:36.660 --> 00:30:47.217
The plan was to take out half.

00:30:47.217 --> 00:31:03.613
I saw Trump crying and asking for mercy for America.

00:31:03.907 --> 00:31:35.696
He was skinnier and looked very worn out, but he was broken to the point of interceding.

00:31:36.068 --> 00:31:59.664
I saw pastors in the Oval Office pacing and praying in the spirit with him.

00:31:59.664 --> 00:32:38.893
I saw a tall, slender pastor with a bald head—he was balder than me on top—praying in a gray suit.

00:32:40.133 --> 00:33:06.800
As they prayed, I saw shockwaves like paddles hitting a nation to wake it up.

00:33:16.619 --> 00:33:16.839
The blackness started to ripple away.

00:33:16.839 --> 00:33:31.415
Then I saw a light in the north like a match.

00:33:36.097 --> 00:34:04.778
The world was covered in blackness, but like a chick breaking out of an egg, the light exploded that blackness off.

00:34:15.730 --> 00:34:16.125
It shattered like ice.

00:34:25.059 --> 00:34:54.187
This intense light, similar to what is at the Father's throne, started sending rays of light through that membrane.

00:34:54.187 --> 00:35:31.080
After I saw all the scenes, I saw men and women of God dressed in white.

00:35:31.080 --> 00:35:46.508
They were saturated in a glow like honey.

00:35:47.554 --> 00:35:59.130
The glory of the Lord was present on them.

00:36:01.644 --> 00:36:29.776
The Lord said this will be the remnant that rises up with a supernatural covering.

00:36:29.776 --> 00:37:03.519
When the plague tries to get on them, it dies because of that honey glow.

00:37:05.334 --> 00:37:18.647
The glory of the Lord kills it.

00:37:35.931 --> 00:38:02.871
He said, 'Son, you will not survive this if you do not have an understanding of the power of the name of Jesus.

00:38:02.871 --> 00:38:52.000
' The people who walk in this will have a revelation of the glory and the Covenant.

00:38:52.000 --> 00:39:03.903
It must be a Rhema word.

00:39:03.903 --> 00:39:27.066
He said if you wait until this is at your door, it will be too late.

00:39:27.066 --> 00:39:39.767
This is a fast development you must take seriously.

00:39:39.767 --> 00:41:02.964
You must bring in the harvest while it is day, for night is coming.

00:41:13.904 --> 00:41:22.972
The window of opportunity is closing.

00:41:22.972 --> 00:42:05.980
Many will not learn how to stand because they are baby Christians, but it's vital they get born again so they don't go to hell.

00:42:05.980 --> 00:42:13.660
Saying the sinner's prayer is everything.

00:42:13.660 --> 00:42:41.594
Our ultimate task is to preach that Jesus Christ is coming and to get people born again.

00:42:41.594 --> 00:43:10.210
If we do not pray to lessen this, many people will die and go to hell.

00:43:10.210 --> 00:43:36.924
This is a stern word, but these people are ruthless.

00:43:57.980 --> 00:44:07.586
The Lord told me to listen to Steve Cioccolanti's sermon about the horses.

00:44:11.794 --> 00:44:20.359
I told him he must preach it more.

00:44:20.959 --> 00:44:37.620
It was a confirmation because he heard it too.

00:44:45.119 --> 00:45:23.560
The Lord said many prophetic voices have a mixture right now; they are not hearing the clear word because they are filled with the praise of man and ego.

00:45:23.560 --> 00:45:32.000
They have 'wax' in their ears.

00:45:32.000 --> 00:45:45.544
They must prophesy from the throne room.

00:45:45.544 --> 00:45:59.400
As you surrender, He will show you what is to come.

00:46:05.067 --> 00:46:12.459
In the last days, there will be plagues, pestilences, and famines.

00:46:12.459 --> 00:46:28.800
Do not focus on that; focus on the task at hand.

00:46:28.800 --> 00:46:55.960
Bring in the lost and teach them their Covenant rights and the authority of the blood of Jesus.

00:47:04.640 --> 00:47:37.880
You must teach my people how to call those things that be not as though they were, and that they have power to tread on serpents and scorpions.

00:47:37.880 --> 00:47:56.579
A thousand shall fall at their side, but nothing shall come nigh them.

00:48:05.830 --> 00:48:22.728
The name of the Lord is a strong tower, and the righteous run into it and are safe.

00:48:22.728 --> 00:48:42.817
We must know the power of communion—that we have a covenant with Him.

00:48:42.817 --> 00:49:08.649
His blood cleanses us and the same power that raised Jesus from the dead dwells in us.

00:49:08.649 --> 00:49:22.920
As He is, so are we in this world.

00:49:22.920 --> 00:49:30.446
If He delivered the children of Israel from the plagues of Egypt, He will deliver you.

00:49:30.446 --> 00:49:49.611
They had the blood on the doorposts, and the death angel passed over.

00:49:50.926 --> 00:50:00.760
We have the ultimate Lamb, Jesus Christ.

00:50:06.100 --> 00:50:31.196
We do not fear plagues because greater is He that is in us than he that is in the world.

00:50:42.288 --> 00:50:58.880
Father, I thank You for the precious blood and the body that was broken for us.

00:51:04.755 --> 00:51:10.154
We have authority in the name of Jesus.

00:51:10.154 --> 00:51:21.580
Any kind of Black Death or pestilence must bow.

00:51:22.240 --> 00:51:38.600
I am not afraid of the terror by night.

00:51:50.540 --> 00:51:57.880
I have such an urgency because this wicked world needs help.

00:51:59.540 --> 00:52:24.573
We stopped so much during the inauguration; we are an army.

00:52:24.573 --> 00:53:07.294
I bring this to you not for fear, but because the Lord said some of this will happen and we can lessen it.

00:53:07.294 --> 00:53:20.299
We have time to prepare; it’s not this year.

00:53:29.531 --> 00:53:50.109
This will be a year of acceleration, wealth, and the glory of the Lord.

00:53:50.109 --> 00:54:04.062
Get your 'Joseph supply' ready and get out of compromise.

00:54:04.062 --> 00:54:21.480
2025, 2026, and 2027 are a window to pray.

00:54:28.646 --> 00:54:35.559
I see things years in the distance.

00:54:51.818 --> 00:54:59.979
I saw a three-month window—March, April, and May—where the bulk of the death occurred.

00:54:59.979 --> 00:55:22.800
It started showing on the news in late October and November.

00:55:22.800 --> 00:55:31.422
Let’s take communion and pray.

00:55:31.422 --> 00:55:50.805
Father, we thank You that by Your stripes we are healed.

00:55:50.805 --> 00:56:01.902
No weapon formed against us shall prosper.

00:56:01.902 --> 00:56:32.799
We thank You for the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous and for a year of great turnaround.

00:56:38.480 --> 00:56:41.652
We are the Josephs of this generation.

00:56:41.652 --> 00:56:54.657
We apply the blood over our houses, marriages, and children.

00:56:54.657 --> 00:57:08.114
We call our unsaved loved ones saved and delivered.

00:57:08.114 --> 00:57:15.914
As we take this blood, it covers us from the top of our heads to the soles of our feet.

00:57:15.914 --> 00:57:29.560
We take authority over every demonic spirit and pestilence.

00:57:29.560 --> 00:57:43.160
We petition You, Lord, to spare these people and call forth mercy.

00:57:43.160 --> 00:57:56.780
We turn this ship around through intercessory prayer.

00:57:56.780 --> 00:58:18.720
We thank You that President Trump is protected and that You will breathe on this nation for a supernatural harvest.

00:58:18.720 --> 00:58:30.782
We call for healing for everyone believing for it right now.

00:58:30.782 --> 00:59:00.297
We are an army and we say this pestilence will not do what I've seen in the name of Jesus.

00:59:00.297 --> 00:59:17.440
We wrestle not against flesh and blood, but against principalities.

00:59:17.440 --> 00:59:37.746
When you see things like what happened in Tennessee, that is a demonic spirit influencing weak minds.

00:59:37.746 --> 00:59:48.069
Take authority over your town and your children's schools.

01:00:02.891 --> 01:00:17.905
Apply the blood over your area and call for a crop failure over the seeds of the enemy.

01:00:17.905 --> 01:00:34.039
Use your anointing oil to symbolize the blood of Jesus.

01:00:44.880 --> 01:00:56.900
Anoint your children’s heads and say, 'No weapon formed against you will prosper.

01:00:56.900 --> 01:01:08.328
' Anoint your house, your doors, and your windows.

01:01:22.359 --> 01:01:22.652
No devil in hell can cross the bloodline.

01:01:22.652 --> 01:01:41.530
Anoint your car so you are protected from car wrecks and calamity.

01:01:41.530 --> 01:01:58.493
Make much of the blood, and the blood will make much of you.

01:01:58.493 --> 01:02:20.733
Even if you face a virus, stand in faith; you are always in the place of victory.

01:02:20.733 --> 01:02:35.960
We are overcomers by the blood of the Lamb.

01:02:35.960 --> 01:02:46.333
Thank you for joining me today.

01:02:46.333 --> 01:02:59.577
If you're new, please subscribe and click the notification bell.

01:02:59.577 --> 01:03:14.194
We have channels in Portuguese, Spanish, Hindi, and many others.

01:03:14.194 --> 01:03:27.540
It's amazing to reach the lost through AI translation.

01:03:48.170 --> 01:03:48.400
We pray for your safety and protection.

01:03:48.400 --> 01:03:57.273
We are victorious because we are Kings' kids.

01:03:57.273 --> 01:04:13.433
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

01:04:13.433 --> 01:04:22.760
Jesus loves you, and we love you.

01:04:29.946 --> 01:04:38.102
God bless you all, and we will see you again soon.

01:04:38.102 --> 01:04:39.606
Bye-bye.
